source.name: National Downloadable File - Simplified View
source.description: This view contains all pertinent details about Physician Compare physicians and other health care professionals but excludes extra numerical identifiers that may be needed for more advanced data manipulation.

datasets.name: National Downloadable File - Extended View
datasets.description: This view contains all data elements available in the Physician Compare National Downloadable File. It is intended for researchers with experience in advanced data manipulation techniques. This view allows researchers to identify all the Medicare enrollments for a single provider and all providers enrolled with a particular group practice. Numerical identifiers for group practices are included to distinguish between groups with similar names.

datasets.name: National Downloadable File
datasets.description: The Physician Compare downloadable file is organized at the individual provider level; each line is unique at the provider/enrollment/organization/address level. Providers with multiple enrollments and/or single enrollments linking to multiple practice location addresses are listed on multiple lines.
